query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('english')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('adverbs',
'american-english',
'commas',
'grammatical-number',
'orthography',
'pronouns',
'punctuation',
'synonyms',
'syntactic-analysis',
'tenses',
'usage',
'vocabulary',
'word-order');
